                                        <div style="font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 4px;">AMS1117-3.3 稳压芯片</div>
                                        <div style="font-size: 12px; color: #666;">型号：AMS1117-3.3 | ¥1.50/个</div>
                                    </td>
